          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#f04e00]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#f04e00]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Contenido Exclusivo</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Canal YouTube con casas de famosos y consejos de inversión</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#f04e00]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#f04e00]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Equipo Especializado</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Expertos en diferentes zonas y tipos de propiedades</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#f04e00]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#f04e00]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
